reviews.content:
I jumped in the deep end with PIRANHA 3DD. Even cheesier then the first movie After the events at Lake Victoria the school of blood-thirsty piranhas make their way to a greasy water park. I'm a fan of the original PIRANHA and the 2010 remake and I didn't mind PIRANHA 3DD more gore, more cheesy, more blood, and lots more double D's. I didn't like the chicks they cast for the virgins trust me they are not believable as virgins and besides the cameos you don't care who lives or dies. As for the cameo's it's a nice set witch makes this movie worth the watch David Koechner, Gary Busey, Paul Scheer, from the first movie Ving Rhames, and David Hasselhoff as HIMSELF! With Christopher Lloyd as the crazy scientists witch is a mix of doc brown and uncle fester. The movie should have been seen in 3D but if you are in the mood for a cheesy B-movie with blood gore and boobs the check out PIRANHA 3DD......cheers and life will never suck as long as there is a movie to watch

5.5 out of 10 
